458
00:37:04,780 --> 00:37:07,640
 Taj koji se udara o prsa, objavlje statuse,

459
00:37:07,640 --> 00:37:09,680
 he, bez, kršćanske,

460
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:13,280
 a kod kući joj možda razapinjemo druge,

461
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:16,500
 u društvu pljujemo po drugima,

462
00:37:16,500 --> 00:37:19,580
 uskraćujemo ljubav drugima,

463
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:21,560
 vrijeme i pažnju,

464
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:24,220
 a svaki dan smo u crkvi.

465
00:37:24,220 --> 00:37:27,900
 Kako? Objasniti.

466
00:37:29,020 --> 00:37:31,700
 Oni nemaju potrebu tražiti.

467
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:33,300
 Milost Božje.

468
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:35,220
 E, sada ću vam reći.

469
00:37:35,220 --> 00:37:37,040
 Šta gospode radi sa takvim?

470
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:41,260
 Mnogi se već raz sigurno pitate,

471
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:43,980
 a zašto me zadesilo to i to?

472
00:37:43,980 --> 00:37:45,640
 Zašto koronavirus?

473
00:37:45,640 --> 00:37:46,720
 Zašto potres?

474
00:37:46,720 --> 00:37:48,560
 Zašto boles?

475
00:37:48,560 --> 00:37:50,020
 Zašto gubitak ovoga?

476
00:37:50,020 --> 00:37:51,900
 Zašto pad u ovome?

477
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:53,220
 Zašto pad u onome?

478
00:37:53,220 --> 00:37:56,880
 Evo sad odgovor ću ti dati.

479
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,960
 Poslušaj riječ Božje.

480
00:37:59,020 --> 00:38:02,540
 Čitam iz knjige Otkrivenja,

481
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:03,960
 koja mi je temelj za argument.

482
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:06,980
 Ne kaže Stjepan, riječ Božje.

483
00:38:06,980 --> 00:38:09,240
 Knjiga Otkrivenja, četvrto poglavlje.

484
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:12,600
 Ti tvrdiš, bogat sam,

485
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:15,280
 nagomilao sam bogatstvo,

486
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:17,020
 ništa mi ne treba,

487
00:38:17,020 --> 00:38:20,440
 a ne znaš da si upravo ti nesretan,

488
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,820
 i bijedan,

489
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:23,580
 i sveromašan,

490
00:38:23,580 --> 00:38:25,100
 i slijep, i gov.

491
00:38:25,100 --> 00:38:28,180
 Savjetujem ti da od mene kupiš

492
00:38:28,180 --> 00:38:30,000
 u vatri žeženoga zlata,

493
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,500
 da se obogatiš,

494
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:33,780
 i da se obučeš u bijele haljine,

495
00:38:33,780 --> 00:38:36,500
 i da se sakriješ svoju sramotu,

496
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:37,340
 golotinju,

497
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:39,780
 zatim pomasti,

498
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:41,620
 da pomažeš svoje oči,

499
00:38:41,620 --> 00:38:42,620
 da bi vidio.

500
00:38:42,620 --> 00:38:44,160
 Dakle,

501
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:45,280
 ovo je odlomak,

502
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:47,640
 gdje se obraća crkvama

503
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:48,660
 u Ladi Ceji,

504
00:38:48,660 --> 00:38:50,200
 u knjigi Otkrivenja,

505
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:52,860
 o kakvom zlatu oni pričaju uopće.

506
00:38:52,860 --> 00:38:56,040
 Bog poziva njih

507
00:38:56,040 --> 00:38:58,620
 da kupe od njega žeženoga zlata.

508
00:38:58,620 --> 00:38:59,620
 Bog.

509
00:38:59,620 --> 00:39:02,240
 Kako zlato Bog nobi?

510
00:39:02,240 --> 00:39:05,340
 Da li vi znate kako nastaje zlata?

511
00:39:05,340 --> 00:39:08,260
 Svi ga nosimo,

512
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:09,320
 vjerovatno na sebi,

513
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:12,420
 svi imate vjerovatno neki dio u kući,

514
00:39:12,420 --> 00:39:14,260
 ne znam, burma,

515
00:39:14,260 --> 00:39:15,880
 da li na ušince, bilo što.

516
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:18,020
 I mi što vidimo zlato,

517
00:39:18,020 --> 00:39:19,100
 vidimo komad zlata.

518
00:39:19,220 --> 00:39:20,320
 Znate li kako nastaje?

519
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:22,360
 Dakle, zlato

520
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:25,180
 se kuha na velikoj temperaturi

521
00:39:25,180 --> 00:39:27,480
 i da bi se pročistilo

522
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:29,940
 pravo, najčistije zlato,

523
00:39:29,940 --> 00:39:32,140
 najčistije zlato,

524
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:34,040
 ono je mekano, elastično,

525
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:34,960
 nećete vjerovat.

526
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:37,480
 Ovo što mi nosimo na sebi,

527
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,640
 ja nemam na sebi ništa,

528
00:39:38,640 --> 00:39:40,160
 ovo što mi nosimo na sebi,

529
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:41,200
 to je tvrdo zlato.

530
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:44,280
 Ali na velikoj temperaturi

531
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:47,120
 se stavlja da bi se pročistilo

532
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:49,400
 od lažnih drugih primjesa.

533
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:52,660
 Bakra, cinka, željeza,

534
00:39:52,660 --> 00:39:55,340
 blata, prljaštine i svega ostalog.

535
00:39:55,340 --> 00:39:55,860
 Kužite.

536
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:59,180
 Kada se stavi na veliku temperaturu,

537
00:39:59,180 --> 00:40:02,900
 na površinu isplivaju sve prljaštine

538
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:05,920
 i na dnu se odvaja zlato čisto,

539
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:07,720
 koje je elastično.

540
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:12,000
 E, to se događa u našem duhovnom životu.

541
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,520
 To, kad tebe zadesi,

542
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:16,340
 kad te zadesi križ,

543
00:40:16,340 --> 00:40:19,340
 kad kuhaš na plamenu,

544
00:40:19,340 --> 00:40:21,240
 gospodin te pročišćava.

545
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:24,400
 Ti, koji si možda ohol kao i ja,

546
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:26,340
 da sam zatražiš,

547
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,940
 gospodine, očisti mi srce,

548
00:40:27,940 --> 00:40:29,720
 molim te od različitih primjesa

549
00:40:29,720 --> 00:40:30,780
 koje u sebi ne vidim,

550
00:40:30,780 --> 00:40:33,800
 gospodin nam pomaže,

551
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:35,780
 on se zauzima za nas,

552
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:37,680
 mene i tebe stavlja

553
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:40,520
 u različite situacije

554
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:42,220
 u kojima nam je zaista teško,

555
00:40:42,220 --> 00:40:44,720
 koje teško proživljavamo.

556
00:40:44,720 --> 00:40:46,380
 A što se tada događa?

557
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:49,720
 Tada se događa da se moji tvoje srce čisti,

558
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:53,160
 postaje elastično poput zlata.

559
00:40:53,160 --> 00:40:55,020
 I zato u knjizi otkrivenja kaže

560
00:40:55,020 --> 00:40:58,400
 dođi da ću vam ja zlata žeženoga

561
00:40:58,400 --> 00:40:59,440
 da vidite.

562
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:03,460
 Dakle, vidite što se događa

563
00:41:03,460 --> 00:41:05,540
 kada mi sami ne želimo tražiti

564
00:41:05,540 --> 00:41:08,000
 milost Božju, da gospodin promieni naše srce.

565
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,820
 Gospodin sam nađe put.

566
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:11,220
 Nađe put

567
00:41:11,220 --> 00:41:14,600
 da nas kroz različite teške situacije

568
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:17,700
 neću reći pritisne,

569
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,520
 gruba je riječ.

570
00:41:18,520 --> 00:41:20,440
 Pomogne nam da rafiniramo

571
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:21,900
 naše srce.

572
00:41:21,900 --> 00:41:22,440
 Razumijete?

573
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:25,520
 Ono što, onaj korak koji mi nikad sami ne bi učinili,

574
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:27,820
 gospodin te stavi da prođeš krodnjega

575
00:41:27,820 --> 00:41:30,860
 i zato ima smisla ona parola kada kažu

576
00:41:30,860 --> 00:41:33,300
 ono što te ne obje to teo jača.

577
00:41:33,300 --> 00:41:35,780
 Osobno sam to doživio.

578
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:37,980
 Nisam nekada razumio,

579
00:41:37,980 --> 00:41:39,780
 Bože, zašto me ješ to moje srce?

580
00:41:39,780 --> 00:41:40,840
 Šta hoćeš od mene?

581
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,640
 Zašto sve ovo moram proći?

582
00:41:43,640 --> 00:41:46,920
 I opet ću ponoviti ono što tisuću puta ponavljam.

583
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:50,840
 Nijednu ozbilju duhovnu stvar

584
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:53,240
 nisam doživio kroz

585
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:55,020
 da-da-da-da-da-da-da

586
00:41:55,020 --> 00:41:56,740
 nego kroz križu.

587
00:41:56,740 --> 00:41:58,780
 Kroz rafiniranje moga srca.

588
00:41:58,780 --> 00:42:01,540
 I nisam zahvalan gospodina

589
00:42:01,540 --> 00:42:02,620
 ako mi da tu milost

590
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:03,900
 da ga još više pročisti.

591
00:42:03,900 --> 00:42:05,380
 Zato večera

592
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:06,880
 slušaš i gledaš ovo

593
00:42:06,880 --> 00:42:07,880
